ComicInfo.Summary: There's an old saying that if Katchoo ever met the "Blue Bird Of Happiness" she'd probably eat it! Well, we have the pictures to prove it. Somebody wants Katchoo dead; somebody she knows and trusts. But who? Katchoo plays a dangerous game of cat-and- mouse with an adversary she can't see, as a rogue DUCk (Deep Underground Parker Girl) stalks her disguised as a trusted friend. But which friend? Can Katchoo uncover the identity of the lethal Judas before it's too late?
ComicInfo.Title: Snow White
